message: Hi Bob, I'm offering my product to you for $9,000. It's a great deal for both of us, as it's worth at least $8,000 to you. Let me know your thoughts!
Hello Alice, thank you for your offer. I understand the value of your product is $8,000 to me, so I would like to propose a counteroffer of $8,500. I hope this is within your acceptable range.
